snippet.title: 28 YEARS LATER - New Trailer
snippet.description:
Danny Boyle and Alex Garland reunite for #28YearsLater – exclusively in movie theatres 6.20. 

Follow Us on Social:
https://twitter.com/28yearslatermov
https://www.facebook.com/28yearslaterofficial
https://www.instagram.com/28yearslatermovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@28yearslatermovie 

28 DAYS LATER is now available to buy or rent on Digital: https://bit.ly/28DaysLaterOnDigital

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Academy Award®-winning director Danny Boyle and Academy Award®-nominated writer Alex Garland reunite for 28 Years Later, a terrifying new story set in the world created by 28 Days Later. It’s been almost three decades since the rage virus escaped a biological weapons laboratory, and now, still in a ruthlessly enforced quarantine, some have found ways to exist amidst the infected. One such group of survivors lives on a small island connected to the mainland by a single, heavily-defended causeway. When one of the group leaves the island on a mission into the dark heart of the mainland, he discovers secrets, wonders, and horrors that have mutated not only the infected but other survivors as well.
 
Directed by:​​
Danny Boyle​​​
​
Written by:​​​​
Alex Garland​​​
 
Produced by: ​​​​
Andrew Macdonald
​​​​​Peter Rice
​​​​​Bernard Bellew
Danny Boyle
Alex Garland
 
Executive Producer:​​​
Cillian Murphy
 
Cast:​
Jodie Comer
​Aaron Taylor-Johnson
​Jack O'Connell
​Alfie Williams
​and Ralph Fiennes
 
This film is not yet rated by The Motion Picture Association. For future rating information, please visit www.filmratings.com.
 
Credits not final

And I’m a gambler I’ll take the over on the underdog

But the night I said I’m leavin’
I turned into Richard Petty
Broke my heart so I got even in my ‘97 Chevy
Now I’m walking on this water mixed with Johnny Walker Black

But the main one is that I ain’t coming back

You call me the devil
Then you told me where to go
Go throw your pebbles

But the main one is that I ain’t coming back

‘Cause the night I said I’m leavin’
I turned into Richard Petty
Broke my heart and I got even in my ‘97 Chevy
Now I’m walking on this water mixed with Johnny Walker Black
There’s a lot of reasons I ain’t Jesus
But the main one is that I ain’t coming back
Oh no no, I ain’t coming back
Ooh

es.title: ¡El equipo de scouts de Pottstown REGRESA en 2025 con una plantilla INCREÍBLEMENTE nueva!
es.description:
¡El equipo de scouts de Pottstown ha vuelto oficialmente! En el video de hoy, les mostramos al nuevo equipo de scouts de Pottstown (12u) jugando en el Complejo Deportivo Boombah en Sanford, Florida. ¡Viva el primer evento del equipo de scouts de Pottstown, donde los jugadores estrenarán todo su equipo nuevo! Después, sígalos en el entrenamiento, donde competirán en desafíos para ganar premios. ¡Después, vean a Pottstown jugar sus dos primeros partidos! ¡Estén atentos al próximo video, que se publicará el sábado 19 de abril a las 8 p. m. (hora del este)!

¡Asegúrense de darle a "me gusta", comentar y suscribirse para participar en el sorteo! ¡Gracias por ver el vídeo!

No te pierdas a @wilsonballgloves, @evoSHIELD y @demarinisports.

¡Un reconocimiento a @ballgloveking por estrenar 17 guantes en 24 horas! ¡No te lo pierdas!

snippet.title: Canada election 2025: English language leaders' debate | FULL
snippet.description:
Liberal Leader Mark Carney sought to cast himself as a safe choice to guide Canada through a crisis during the English-language debate on Thursday evening.

Carney, currently leading in the polls, was the primary target during the final debate of the election, with his chief rival Conservative Party Leader Pierre Poilievre trying to paint him as “more of the same” following a decade of Liberal leadership.

“Mr. Carney, Justin Trudeau’s staffers are actually here with you at this debate in Montreal, writing the talking points that you are regurgitating into the microphone,” he said.

Carney, who tried to differentiate himself from former prime minister Justin Trudeau, retorted: “Look, I do my own talking points thank you.”

Later in the debate, NDP Leader Jagmeet Singh accused Carney of failing to defend Canadian jobs threatened by U.S. tariffs.

Bloc Quebecois Leader Yves-Francois Blanchet, meanwhile, argued that Carney must disclose his financial assets to show he’s better than Trudeau, picking up on an issue that has dogged Carney throughout the campaign.

00:00 Group photo
7:51 Debate begins
8:39 Tariffs and threats to Canada
26:07 Affordability and the cost of living
44:47 Public safety and security
1:04:02 Energy and climate
1:21:48 Leading in a Crisis

Buchen Sie den Millennial Farmer als Redner für Ihre nächste Veranstaltung:
►mnmillennialfarmer@gmail.com

Zach Johnson, der „Millennial Farmer“, ist Landwirt in fünfter Generation und hat sein Leben lang auf dem Bauernhof seiner Familie gepflanzt, gearbeitet und gelernt. Sein Witz und sein trockener Humor sprechen Kinder und Erwachsene gleichermaßen an. Als Kind der Millennial-Generation verbindet sich seine Wertschätzung für neue Technologien mit seiner traditionellen Arbeitsmoral. Er verfügt über die einzigartige Fähigkeit, seine Botschaft so zu vermitteln, dass sie sowohl langjährige Landwirte als auch Menschen ohne landwirtschaftliche Kenntnisse anspricht. Angesichts des wachsenden Bewusstseins der Verbraucher für die Herkunft ihrer Lebensmittel hat Zach erkannt, dass eine unabhängige Stimme aus der Landwirtschaft benötigt wird. Zach fördert aktiv die Landwirtschaft, indem er seine täglichen Erfahrungen in der Landwirtschaft teilt und gleichzeitig Landwirte für Landwirte schult, um den Dialog zwischen Landwirten und der Öffentlichkeit zu fördern.

Folgen Sie uns
►https://www.instagram.com/mnmillennialfarmer/ ►https://www.facebook.com/MNMILLENNIALFARMER/
►https://twitter.com/farmmillennial
►https://www.tiktok.com/@millennialfarmer

-Lauren e Arie Luyendyk

snippet.title: What I Saw in Antarctica
snippet.description:
A big thank you to FUTURE of SPACE and their Media Team for capturing and contributing stunning visuals from this extraordinary voyage.

FUTURE of SPACE is a media/production company dedicated to creating original content, immersive programs, and experiential events that explore new frontiers, celebrate the human experience, and elevate global conversations. Through groundbreaking initiatives like Space2Sea, FoS connects diverse voices to inspire curiosity, innovation, and a more connected future.

Media Team Credit:  Brendan Hall, Gabriella Canal, Tyler Brower

Follow FUTURE of SPACE for more visionary content and experiences ahead:
Website: https://futureofspace.io 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/futureofspace.io/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/people/futureofspaceio/61566710741346/
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@FUTUREofSPACE_official

What does Neil deGrasse Tyson do on a trip to Antarctica? On this special episode, Neil deGrasse Tyson recounts his trip to Antarctica, where he walked with penguins, crossed the Drake Passage, and took a deep-sea dive into the alien Antarctic waters. 

Timestamps: 
00:00 - Introduction: Antarctica
3:47 - Crossing Drake’s Passage
4:58 - On Exploration & Discovery
8:23 - The Cold & Ice
12:56 - Tabletop Icebergs
14:00 - Neil’s Underwater Experiment
17:42 - Breaking the Ice Sheets
20:48 - Penguin Land

Check out our second channel, @StarTalkPlus

About StarTalk: 
Science meets pop culture on StarTalk! Astrophysicist & Hayden Planetarium director Neil deGrasse Tyson, his comic co-hosts, guest celebrities & scientists discuss astronomy, physics, and everything else about life in the universe. Keep Looking Up!

hi.title: अंटार्कटिका में मैंने क्या देखा
hi.description:
इस असाधारण यात्रा से आश्चर्यजनक दृश्यों को कैप्चर करने और योगदान देने के लिए FUTURE of SPACE और उनकी मीडिया टीम को बहुत-बहुत धन्यवाद।

FUTURE of SPACE एक मीडिया/प्रोडक्शन कंपनी है जो मूल सामग्री, इमर्सिव प्रोग्राम और अनुभवात्मक कार्यक्रम बनाने के लिए समर्पित है जो नई सीमाओं का पता लगाते हैं, मानवीय अनुभव का जश्न मनाते हैं और वैश्विक बातचीत को आगे बढ़ाते हैं। Space2Sea जैसी अभूतपूर्व पहलों के माध्यम से, FoS जिज्ञासा, नवाचार और अधिक जुड़े हुए भविष्य को प्रेरित करने के लिए विविध आवाज़ों को जोड़ता है।

मीडिया टीम क्रेडिट: ब्रेंडन हॉल, गैब्रिएला कैनाल, टायलर ब्रॉवर

भविष्य के भविष्य के लिए अधिक दूरदर्शी सामग्री और अनुभवों के लिए FUTURE of SPACE को फ़ॉलो करें:
वेबसाइट: https://futureofspace.io

इंस्टाग्राम: https://www.instagram.com/futureofspace.io/
फेसबुक: https://www.facebook.com/people/futureofspaceio/61566710741346/
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@FUTUREofSPACE_official

नील डीग्रास टायसन अंटार्कटिका की यात्रा पर क्या करते हैं? इस विशेष एपिसोड में, नील डीग्रास टायसन अंटार्कटिका की अपनी यात्रा के बारे में बताते हैं, जहाँ उन्होंने पेंगुइन के साथ सैर की, ड्रेक पैसेज को पार किया और विदेशी अंटार्कटिक जल में गहरे समुद्र में गोता लगाया।

14:00 - नील का पानी के नीचे का प्रयोग

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/startalk

स्टारटॉक पर विज्ञान और पॉप संस्कृति का मिलन! खगोलशास्त्री और हेडन प्लेनेटेरियम के निदेशक नील डीग्रास टायसन, उनके कॉमिक सह-मेजबान, अतिथि हस्तियाँ और वैज्ञानिक खगोल विज्ञान, भौतिकी और ब्रह्मांड में जीवन के बारे में बाकी सब कुछ पर चर्चा करते हैं। ऊपर देखते रहो!

de-DE.title: Was ich in der Antarktis gesehen habe
de-DE.description:
Ein großes Dankeschön an FUTURE of SPACE und sein Medienteam für die beeindruckenden Bilder dieser außergewöhnlichen Reise.

FUTURE of SPACE ist ein Medien- und Produktionsunternehmen, das sich der Entwicklung origineller Inhalte, immersiver Programme und Erlebnisveranstaltungen widmet, die neue Grenzen erkunden, die menschliche Erfahrung würdigen und globale Gespräche fördern. Durch bahnbrechende Initiativen wie Space2Sea verbindet FoS vielfältige Stimmen, um Neugier, Innovation und eine vernetztere Zukunft zu fördern.

Medienteam: Brendan Hall, Gabriella Canal, Tyler Brower

Was macht Neil deGrasse Tyson auf einer Reise in die Antarktis? In dieser Sonderfolge erzählt Neil deGrasse Tyson von seiner Reise in die Antarktis, wo er mit Pinguinen spazieren ging, die Drakestraße durchquerte und einen Tiefseetauchgang in die fremdartigen Gewässer der Antarktis unternahm.

Wissenschaft trifft Pop Kultur auf StarTalk! Der Astrophysiker und Leiter des Hayden Planetariums Neil deGrasse Tyson diskutiert mit seinen Co-Moderatoren, prominenten Gästen und Wissenschaftlern über Astronomie, Physik und alles rund um das Leben im Universum. Schaut weiter nach oben!

#StarTalk #NeildeGrasseTyson

fr-FR.title: Ce que j'ai vu en Antarctique
fr-FR.description:
Un grand merci à FUTURE of SPACE et à son équipe média pour avoir capturé et contribué aux images époustouflantes de ce voyage extraordinaire.

FUTURE of SPACE est une société de production et de médias dédiée à la création de contenus originaux, de programmes immersifs et d'événements expérientiels qui explorent de nouvelles frontières, célèbrent l'expérience humaine et enrichissent les échanges internationaux. Grâce à des initiatives innovantes comme Space2Sea, FoS rassemble des voix diverses pour susciter la curiosité, l'innovation et un avenir plus connecté.

Crédits média : Brendan Hall, Gabriella Canal, Tyler Brower

Suivez FUTURE of SPACE pour découvrir d'autres contenus et expériences visionnaires :
Site web : https://futureofspace.io
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/futureofspace.io/
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/people/futureofspaceio/61566710741346/
YouTube : https://www.youtube.com/@FUTUREofSPACE_official

Que fait Neil deGrasse Tyson lors d'un voyage en Antarctique ? Dans cet épisode spécial, Neil deGrasse Tyson raconte son voyage en Antarctique, où il a marché avec des manchots, traversé le passage de Drake et plongé dans les eaux lointaines de l'Antarctique.

Horodatage :
00:00 - Introduction : Antarctique
3:47 - Traversée du passage de Drake
4:58 - Exploration et découverte
8:23 - Froid et glace
12:56 - Icebergs de table
14:00 - L’expérience sous-marine de Neil
17:42 - Briser la banquise
20:48 - Le pays des pingouins

Découvrez notre deuxième chaîne, @StarTalkPlus

Procurez-vous le NOUVEAU livre StarTalk, « Vers l’infini et au-delà : Un voyage vers la découverte cosmique » sur Amazon : https://amzn.to/3PL0NFn

Soutenez-nous sur Patreon : https://www.patreon.com/startalkradio

SUIVEZ ou ABONNEZ-VOUS à StarTalk :
Twitter : http://twitter.com/startalkradio
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/StarTalk

À propos de StarTalk :
La science rencontre la culture populaire sur StarTalk ! L’astrophysicien et directeur du planétarium Hayden, Neil deGrasse Tyson, ses co-animateurs humoristiques, des célébrités invitées et des scientifiques discutent d’astronomie, de physique et de tout ce qui touche à la vie dans l’univers. Continuez à regarder vers le haut !

#StarTalk #NeildeGrasseTyson

ja.title: 南極で見たもの
ja.description:
この特別な航海の素晴らしい映像を撮影し、提供してくださったFUTURE of SPACEとそのメディアチームに心から感謝いたします。

FUTURE of SPACEは、新たな境地を探求し、人類の経験を称え、地球規模の対話を促進する、オリジナルコンテンツ、没入型プログラム、体験型イベントの制作に尽力するメディア／制作会社です。Space2Seaのような画期的な取り組みを通じて、FUTURE of SPACEは多様な声を繋ぎ、好奇心、イノベーション、そしてより繋がりのある未来を育みます。

メディアチーム クレジット: ブレンダン・ホール、ガブリエラ・カナル、タイラー・ブラウアー

FUTURE of SPACE をフォローして、今後の革新的なコンテンツや体験をご覧ください。

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/people/futureofspaceio/61566710741346/
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@FUTUREofSPACE_official

ニール・ドグラース・タイソンは南極旅行で何をするのでしょうか？ この特別エピソードでは、ニール・ドグラース・タイソンが南極旅行の思い出を語ります。ペンギンと歩いたり、ドレーク海峡を横断したり、未知の南極海への深海潜水に挑戦したりしました。

タイムスタンプ：

4:58 - 探検と発見について

20:48 - ペンギンランド

StarTalkについて：スタートークで科学とポップカルチャーが融合！天体物理学者でヘイデン・プラネタリウム館長のニール・ドグラース・タイソンが、コメディアンの共演者、ゲストの著名人、そして科学者たちと、天文学、物理学、そして宇宙における生命について語り合います。空を見上げ続けましょう！

snippet.title: Inside Lenny Kravitz’s Regal Paris Home | Open Door | Architectural Digest
snippet.description:
Today, AD is welcomed by Lenny Kravitz to tour his regal home in Paris. The superstar musician has loved Paris since he first visited in 1989 but it wasn’t until the early 2000s that he decided it was time to get a place in the city. With a small apartment on the Seine in mind, Kravitz's vision deviated a little when he ended up viewing the grand mansion of Countess Anne d’Ornano. Having started his AD100 studio, Kravitz Design, Lenny spearheaded the design of his home. Soulful elegance was Kravitz’s design philosophy, filling his home with photographs, artwork, and artifacts connecting him to his ancestors and influential figures from throughout his life. However, the true heart and soul of the house lies downstairs in the boiler room Kravitz converted into his own speakeasy-style club.

See more of the musician's Paris home: https://www.architecturaldigest.com/gallery/inside-lenny-kravitzs-paris-refuge 

Shop picks inspired by the musician’s home:
https://www.architecturaldigest.com/shopping/lenny-kravitz-open-door

Artwork © Nathaniel Mary Quinn

snippet.title: We left 1 4WD on the track... our 24hr rescue mission
snippet.description:
We left 1 4WD on the track... Our 24hr rescue mission.

We set out to tackle one of Australia’s toughest 4WD tracks — Six Stage. 🔥 A brutal 1km climb with six of the gnarliest challenges you’ll find. It’s been a dream of Shauno’s for years… but he’s never attempted it, until now…

What started as a mission to reach a speccy camp has quickly turned into a night run rescue mission, with a busted rig halfway up and no way out under its own steam. 

This track isn’t for the faint-hearted… If you’re not twin locked & on 35s, don’t even bother. But we’ve taken the turnoff & the boys are frothing for what’s ahead. 

Shaun, Graham, Jock, & Jesse - formerly with 4WD Action - have been delivering the best off-road content in Australia for 20+ years. From epic car builds & 4x4 tips to exploring iconic spots like Fraser Island, Utah, The Kimberley, Colorado, The Rubicon Trail & The Simpson Desert, we create content for every off-roader. We've even hit the tracks with the legends from Donut Media! Whether you’re rocking a fully modified Toyota LandCruiser or just getting started with your Hilux or Ranger, we’ve got you covered for all things 4WD and adventure.

id.title: Kami meninggalkan 1 4WD di lintasan... misi penyelamatan 24 jam kami
id.description:
Kami meninggalkan 1 4WD di lintasan... Misi penyelamatan 24 jam kami.

Kami berangkat untuk menaklukkan salah satu lintasan 4WD terberat di Australia — Six Stage. 🔥 Pendakian brutal sejauh 1 km dengan enam tantangan terberat yang akan Anda temukan. Itu adalah impian Shauno selama bertahun-tahun... tetapi dia tidak pernah mencobanya, sampai sekarang...

Apa yang dimulai sebagai misi untuk mencapai perkemahan khusus telah dengan cepat berubah menjadi misi penyelamatan malam hari, dengan rig yang rusak di tengah jalan dan tidak ada jalan keluar dengan sendirinya.

Lintasan ini bukan untuk orang yang lemah hati... Jika Anda tidak terkunci ganda & menggunakan 35, jangan repot-repot. Tetapi kami telah mengambil jalan keluar & para lelaki bersemangat untuk apa yang ada di depan.

Shaun, Graham, Jock, & Jesse - sebelumnya dengan 4WD Action - telah memberikan konten off-road terbaik di Australia selama 20+ tahun. Dari pembuatan mobil epik & tips 4x4 hingga menjelajahi tempat-tempat ikonik seperti Fraser Island, Utah, The Kimberley, Colorado, The Rubicon Trail & The Simpson Desert, kami membuat konten untuk setiap pengendara off-road. Kami bahkan telah menjelajahi trek dengan para legenda dari Donut Media! Baik Anda menggunakan Toyota LandCruiser yang dimodifikasi sepenuhnya atau baru saja memulai dengan Hilux atau Ranger, kami siap membantu Anda untuk semua hal yang berhubungan dengan 4WD dan petualangan.

hi.title: हमने 1 4WD को ट्रैक पर छोड़ दिया... हमारा 24 घंटे का बचाव अभियान
hi.description:
हमने ट्रैक पर 1 4WD छोड़ दिया... हमारा 24 घंटे का बचाव अभियान।

हम ऑस्ट्रेलिया के सबसे कठिन 4WD ट्रैक में से एक - सिक्स स्टेज पर जाने के लिए तैयार हैं। 🔥 एक क्रूर 1 किमी की चढ़ाई जिसमें छह सबसे कठिन चुनौतियाँ हैं। यह शॉनो का सालों से सपना रहा है... लेकिन उसने अब तक कभी इसका प्रयास नहीं किया...

जो एक स्पेसी कैंप तक पहुँचने के मिशन के रूप में शुरू हुआ था, वह जल्दी ही एक रात के बचाव अभियान में बदल गया, जिसमें आधे रास्ते में एक टूटी हुई रिग थी और अपने आप बाहर निकलने का कोई रास्ता नहीं था।

यह ट्रैक कमज़ोर दिल वालों के लिए नहीं है... अगर आप ट्विन लॉक नहीं हैं और 35 पर हैं, तो परेशान न हों। लेकिन हमने टर्नऑफ़ ले लिया है और लड़के आगे क्या होने वाला है, इसके लिए उत्साहित हैं।

शॉन, ग्राहम, जॉक और जेसी - जो पहले 4WD एक्शन के साथ थे - 20+ सालों से ऑस्ट्रेलिया में सबसे अच्छी ऑफ-रोड सामग्री दे रहे हैं। शानदार कार निर्माण और 4x4 टिप्स से लेकर फ्रेजर आइलैंड, यूटा, द किम्बरली, कोलोराडो, द रूबिकॉन ट्रेल और द सिम्पसन डेजर्ट जैसे प्रतिष्ठित स्थानों की खोज तक, हम हर ऑफ-रोडर के लिए कंटेंट बनाते हैं। हमने डोनट मीडिया के दिग्गजों के साथ ट्रैक पर भी धूम मचाई है! चाहे आप पूरी तरह से मॉडिफाइड टोयोटा लैंडक्रूजर चला रहे हों या अपनी हिलक्स या रेंजर के साथ शुरुआत कर रहे हों, हमने आपको 4WD और एडवेंचर से जुड़ी सभी चीज़ों के लिए कवर किया है।

de-DE.title: Wir haben einen Geländewagen auf der Strecke zurückgelassen... unsere 24-Stunden-Rettungsmission
de-DE.description:
Wir haben einen Geländewagen auf der Strecke gelassen ... Unsere 24-Stunden-Rettungsmission.

Wir haben uns aufgemacht, eine der härtesten Geländewagenstrecken Australiens zu bewältigen – Six Stage. 🔥 Ein brutaler, 1 km langer Anstieg mit sechs der kniffligsten Herausforderungen, die es gibt. Shauno träumt schon seit Jahren davon ... aber er hat es noch nie gewagt, bis jetzt ...

Was als Mission begann, ein Speziallager zu erreichen, entwickelte sich schnell zu einer nächtlichen Rettungsmission, mit einem kaputten Fahrzeug auf halber Höhe, das aus eigener Kraft nicht mehr herauskam.

Diese Strecke ist nichts für schwache Nerven ... Wenn ihr nicht mit Doppelverriegelung und 35er-Reifen unterwegs seid, lasst es bleiben. Aber wir haben die Abzweigung genommen, und die Jungs sind schon ganz heiß auf das, was vor uns liegt.

Shaun, Graham, Jock und Jesse – früher bei 4WD Action – liefern seit über 20 Jahren die besten Offroad-Inhalte Australiens. Von epischen Autoumbauten und 4x4-Tipps bis hin zur Erkundung legendärer Orte wie Fraser Island, Utah, der Kimberley, Colorado, dem Rubicon Trail und der Simpson Desert – wir erstellen Inhalte für jeden Offroader. Wir waren sogar schon mit den Legenden von Donut Media auf der Strecke! Egal, ob du einen komplett modifizierten Toyota LandCruiser fährst oder gerade erst mit deinem Hilux oder Ranger loslegst – bei uns findest du alles rund um Allrad und Abenteuer.

ja.title: 4WD1台をトラックに残しました...24時間救助ミッション
ja.description:
4WD車1台をコース上に置き去りに…24時間レスキューミッション。

オーストラリアで最も過酷な4WDコースの一つ、シックスステージに挑戦することにしました。🔥 全長1kmの過酷な登り坂で、6つの難関が待ち受けています。これはショーノの長年の夢でしたが…今まで一度も挑戦したことがありませんでした…

当初は、スペシーキャンプへのミッションとして始まったものが、登りの途中で故障した車が自力で脱出できないという、夜間走行でのレスキューミッションへと変わりました。

このコースは気の弱い人には向きません…ツインロックで35sタイヤを履いていないなら、挑戦は諦めてください。でも、私たちは分岐を抜け出し、これから起こる出来事に興奮しています。

ショーン、グラハム、ジョック、ジェシーは、元4WDアクションのメンバーで、20年以上にわたりオーストラリアで最高のオフロードコンテンツを提供してきました。壮大な車の組み立てや4WDのヒントから、ユタ州のフレーザー島、コロラド州のキンバリー、ルビコントレイル、シンプソン砂漠といった象徴的なスポットの探索まで、あらゆるオフロードライダーのためのコンテンツを制作しています。Donut Mediaのレジェンドたちと一緒にサーキットを走ったこともあります！フル改造されたトヨタ・ランドクルーザーに乗っている方も、ハイラックスやレンジャーに乗り始めたばかりの方も、4WDとアドベンチャーに関するあらゆる情報を網羅しています。

it.title: Abbiamo lasciato un fuoristrada sulla pista... la nostra missione di salvataggio di 24 ore
it.description:
Abbiamo lasciato un fuoristrada in pista... La nostra missione di salvataggio di 24 ore.

Ci siamo messi in viaggio per affrontare uno dei percorsi fuoristrada più impegnativi d'Australia: Six Stage. 🔥 Una salita brutale di 1 km con sei delle sfide più impegnative che si possano trovare. È un sogno di Shauno da anni... ma non ci ha mai provato, fino ad ora...

Quella che è iniziata come una missione per raggiungere un campo base si è rapidamente trasformata in una missione di salvataggio notturna, con un mezzo rotto a metà strada e senza via d'uscita.

Questo percorso non è per i deboli di cuore... Se non avete il twin lock e le ruote da 35, non preoccupatevi nemmeno. Ma abbiamo preso la deviazione e i ragazzi sono impazienti per quello che ci aspetta.

Shaun, Graham, Jock e Jesse - ex membri di 4WD Action - offrono i migliori contenuti fuoristrada in Australia da oltre 20 anni. Da epiche creazioni di auto e consigli per il fuoristrada all'esplorazione di luoghi iconici come Fraser Island, nello Utah, il Kimberley, in Colorado, il Rubicon Trail e il Simpson Desert, creiamo contenuti per ogni appassionato di fuoristrada. Abbiamo persino percorso le piste con le leggende di Donut Media! Che tu guidi un Toyota Land Cruiser completamente modificato o che tu stia appena iniziando a guidare il tuo Hilux o Ranger, abbiamo tutto ciò che ti serve per il fuoristrada e l'avventura.

fr-FR.title: Nous avons laissé 1 4x4 sur la piste... notre mission de sauvetage de 24 heures
fr-FR.description:
Nous avons laissé un 4x4 sur la piste… Notre mission de sauvetage de 24 heures.

Nous nous sommes lancés à l'assaut de l'un des circuits 4x4 les plus difficiles d'Australie : Six Stage. 🔥 Une montée brutale d'un kilomètre avec six des défis les plus difficiles que vous puissiez rencontrer. Shauno en rêvait depuis des années… mais il ne l'avait jamais tenté, jusqu'à maintenant…

Ce qui a commencé comme une mission pour atteindre un campement spécialisé s'est rapidement transformé en une mission de sauvetage nocturne, avec un véhicule cassé à mi-chemin et aucune issue par ses propres moyens.

Ce circuit n'est pas pour les âmes sensibles… Si vous n'avez pas de bicylindre et de 35 pouces, pas la peine. Mais nous avons pris la sortie et les gars sont impatients de découvrir ce qui les attend.

Shaun, Graham, Jock et Jesse – anciennement de 4WD Action – proposent le meilleur contenu tout-terrain d'Australie depuis plus de 20 ans. Des constructions automobiles épiques aux conseils 4x4, en passant par l'exploration de lieux emblématiques comme Fraser Island (Utah), le Kimberley (Colorado), le Rubicon Trail et le désert de Simpson, nous créons du contenu pour tous les passionnés de tout-terrain. Nous avons même participé à des aventures avec les légendes de Donut Media ! Que vous soyez au volant d'un Toyota LandCruiser entièrement modifié ou que vous débutiez avec votre Hilux ou Ranger, nous avons tout ce qu'il vous faut pour tout ce qui concerne le 4x4 et l'aventure.

en.title: We left 1 4WD on the track... our 24hr rescue mission
en.description:
We left 1 4WD on the track... Our 24hr rescue mission.

We set out to tackle one of Australia’s toughest 4WD tracks — Six Stage. 🔥 A brutal 1km climb with six of the gnarliest challenges you’ll find. It’s been a dream of Shauno’s for years… but he’s never attempted it, until now…

What started as a mission to reach a speccy camp has quickly turned into a night run rescue mission, with a busted rig halfway up and no way out under its own steam. 

This track isn’t for the faint-hearted… If you’re not twin locked & on 35s, don’t even bother. But we’ve taken the turnoff & the boys are frothing for what’s ahead. 

Shaun, Graham, Jock, & Jesse - formerly with 4WD Action - have been delivering the best off-road content in Australia for 20+ years. From epic car builds & 4x4 tips to exploring iconic spots like Fraser Island, Utah, The Kimberley, Colorado, The Rubicon Trail & The Simpson Desert, we create content for every off-roader. We've even hit the tracks with the legends from Donut Media! Whether you’re rocking a fully modified Toyota LandCruiser or just getting started with your Hilux or Ranger, we’ve got you covered for all things 4WD and adventure.

snippet.title: GRIZZLIES at WARRIORS | #SoFiPlayIn | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | April 15, 2025
snippet.description:
The Golden State Warriors defeated the Memphis Grizzlies, 121-116. Stephen Curry (37 points, 8 rebounds, 4 assists) and Jimmy Butler III (38 points, 7 rebounds, 6 assists) combine for 75 points to lead the Warriors to the win. Despite the loss, Desmond Bane totaled 30 points (5 3PM) while Ja Morant added 22 points. The Warriors clinch the #7 seed and will face the #2 Houston Rockets while the Grizzlies will face the winner of the #9 seed Kings and #10 seed Mavericks on Friday for the #8 seed in the Western Conference.

snippet.title: Baldur’s Gate 3: The Final Patch - An Animated Short
snippet.description:
After a lot of testing and a healthy dose of stress, the party are readying for one last adventure to mark the end of an era. But something feels different…

To help us close the door on our last major patch, the party are back with their final animated short in collaboration with Spud Gun Studios (https://www.spudgunstudios.com/), with a special appearance by the man in metal himself: Swen in his animated debut!

snippet.title: THE LIFE OF CHUCK - Official Trailer - In Theaters June
snippet.description:
From the hearts and minds of Stephen King and Mike Flanagan comes THE LIFE OF CHUCK, the extraordinary story of an ordinary man. This unforgettable, genre-bending tale celebrates the life of Charles 'Chuck' Krantz as he experiences the wonder of love, the heartbreak of loss, and the multitudes contained in all of us. 

In Select Cities 6.6, Everywhere 6.13

Directed by
Mike Flanagan

Starring
Tom Hiddleston
Chiwetel Ejiofor
Karen Gillan
Jacob Tremblay
Mark Hamill

In Select Cities 6.6, Everywhere 6.13

Directed by
Mike Flanagan

de.title: UNSER ALLERERSTES P2W-COMMUNITY-EREIGNIS?!
de.description:
Es ist das ... PLAY-TO-WIN-COMMUNITY-EREIGNIS! 🥵🔥

Du hast zehn Tage Zeit, um so viele Belohnungen wie möglich zu erhalten, unter anderem eine ULTRA-TROPHÄENBOX! 😱

🎯 Wir erfassen TAKEDOWNS! Du musst also nur andere Brawler ^£#$!
🔓 Jeder Meilenstein erfordert eine Milliarde Takedowns und nach Erreichen eines Meilensteins kannst du die Belohnungen nach der nächsten täglichen Aktualisierung des Shops abholen!
🙌 Für dieses Ereignis gibt es kein Limit an Belohnungen – das einzige Limit ist die Zeit!

✨BESONDERES GIVEAWAY✨

🎫 Du kannst den Brawlpass Plus für ein GANZES Jahr gewinnen (insgesamt zwölf Pässe!) und außerdem zehn Brawlpässe Plus zum Teilen mit deinen Freunden! 🤯
👀 WIE? Poste deinen besten Spielzug mit dem Hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W auf Social Media. Wir wählen die fünf glücklichen Gewinner nach dem Ende des Ereignisses aus!

it.title: IL PRIMO EVENTO PxV DELLA COMMUNITY!
it.description:
Scopri l'evento della community PARTECIPA PER VINCERE! 🥵🔥

Hai 10 giorni per accumulare quante più ricompense possibili, tra cui una CASSA ULTRA DEI TROFEI! 😱

🎯 Terremo il conto delle ELIMINAZIONI, perciò ti dovrai solo concentrare e fare il ^£#$ a un bel po' di brawler nemici!
🔓 Per raggiungere ogni traguardo, servirà un miliardo di eliminazioni e, una volta sbloccata la ricompensa corrispondente, la potrai ritirare dal negozio non appena si aggiornano le sue offerte.
🙌 In questo evento, le ricompense accumulabili sono infinite! L'unico limite è il tempo.

✨IL CONCORSO SPECIALE✨

🎫 Potrai vincere un anno INTERO di Brawl Pass Plus (ben 12 in totale) e altri 10 Brawl Pass Plus da condividere con gli amici! 🤯
👀 VUOI PARTECIPARE ANCHE TU? Pubblica la tua giocata migliore sui social includendo nel post l'hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W e, alla fine dell'evento, sceglieremo i cinque vincitori!

fr.title: NOTRE TOUT PREMIER ÉVÉNEMENT COMMUNAUTAIRE P2W ?!
fr.description:
Voici... L'ÉVÉNEMENT COMMUNAUTAIRE PLAY TO WIN ! 🥵🔥

Vous avez 10 jours pour gagner autant de récompenses que possible, y compris une ULTRA BOÎTE DES TROPHÉES ! 😱

🎯 C'est les éliminations qui comptent, donc tout ce que vous avez à faire, c'est de ^£#$ des brawlers !
🔓 Vous atteignez chaque palier au bout d'un milliard d'éliminations. Vous pourrez récupérer les récompenses des paliers atteints à la prochaine réinitialisation quotidienne du magasin !
🙌 Il n'y a pas de limite de récompenses pour cet événement, seul le temps est limité !

✨CONCOURS SPÉCIAL✨

🎫 Vous pouvez gagner une année entière de Pass Brawl Plus (12 au total !) + 10 Pass Brawl Plus à partager avec vos amis ! 🤯
👀 COMMENT FAIRE ? Partagez vos plus belles actions sur les réseaux avec le hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W et nous choisirons les 5 gagnants après la fin de l'événement !

ru.title: ПЕРВОЕ В ИСТОРИИ СОБЫТИЕ СООБЩЕСТВА P2W?!
ru.description:
Встречайте... СОБЫТИЕ СООБЩЕСТВА PLAY TO WIN — «ИГРАЙ, ЧТОБЫ ПОБЕДИТЬ!» 🥵🔥

У вас будет 10 дней на получение наград, в числе которых — трофейный ультраящик! 😱

🎯 В этом событии мы считаем победы над бойцами, так что ваша задача — ^£#$ других бойцов!
🔓 Для каждого рубежа нужно набрать 1 миллиард побед, а после его достижения вы сможете забрать награды со следующим обновлением магазина.
🙌 В этом событии нет ограничений на награды — только на время!

✨ОСОБАЯ РАЗДАЧА ПОДАРКОВ✨

🎫 Вы можете выиграть годовой запас Brawl Pass Plus (всего 12 пропусков), а также 10 Brawl Pass Plus в подарок для своих друзей! 🤯
👀 КАК? Поделитесь записью своего лучшего игрового момента в соцсети, добавив хэштег #BrawlStarsP2W, и мы выберем 5 победителей в конце события!

tr.title: İLK P2W TOPLULUK ETKİNLİĞİMİZ!
tr.description:
KAZANMAK İÇİN OYNA TOPLULUK ETKİNLİĞİ başlıyor! 🥵🔥

Bir ULTRA KUPA KUTUSU da dahil, olabildiğince fazla ödül almak için 10 gününüz var! 😱

🎯 YOK ETTİĞİNİZ RAKİPLERİ sayıyoruz! Tek yapmanız gereken diğer savaşçıların hakkından gelmek!
🔓 Her eşik için 1 milyar rakip yok etmeniz gerekiyor ve eşiklere ulaştıktan sonra kazandığınız ödülleri dükkandaki ödüller yenilendiğinde alabileceksiniz!
🙌 Bu etkinlikte ödül sınırı yok, tek sınır süre!

✨ÖZEL ÇEKİLİŞ✨

🎫 Kendiniz için BÜTÜN bir yıllık (toplam 12 adet!) Brawl Pass Plus ve arkadaşlarınızla paylaşabileceğiniz 10 Brawl Pass Plus kazanabilirsiniz! 🤯
👀 NASIL MI? Oyundaki en iyi anlarınızı #BrawlStarsP2W etiketini kullanarak sosyal medya hesabınızda paylaşın. Etkinlik sona erdiğinde beş şanslı kazananı seçeceğiz!

ko.title: 브롤스타즈 사상 최초의 과금 커뮤니티 이벤트?!
ko.description:
사실은... '과하게 금 같은' 커뮤니티 이벤트랍니다! 🥵🔥

10일 동안 울트라 트로피 상자를 비롯해 최대한 많은 보상을 챙기세요! 😱

🎯 이번 이벤트에서는 테이크다운을 집계합니다! 그러니 다른 브롤러를 처치하기만 하면 되는 거죠!
🔓 마일스톤당 10억 테이크다운이 필요하며, 마일스톤 하나를 완료하면 다음 상점 새로고침 후에 보상을 수령할 수 있습니다!
🙌 이번 이벤트는 보상 한도가 없으며, 시간 제한만 있습니다!

✨특별 선물✨

🎫 1년 내내 브롤 패스 플러스(총 12개)를 받을 기회를 잡으세요! 게다가 덤으로, 친구에게 나눠줄 수 있는 10개의 브롤 패스 플러스도 드립니다! 🤯
👀 참여 방법: 소셜 미디어에서 게시물에 #BrawlStarsP2W 해시태그를 사용해 최고의 플레이 장면을 공유하세요. 이벤트 종료 후 행운의 당첨자 5명을 선정할 예정입니다!

es.title: ¿EL PRIMER EVENTO DE LA COMUNIDAD P2W?
es.description:
¡Llega el evento de la comunidad Play to Win (juega para ganar)! 🥵🔥

Consigue todas las recompensas que puedas en 10 días, entre ellas, ¡una caja de trofeos ultra! 😱

🎯 Llevaremos la cuenta de las eliminaciones. ¡Así que ya sabes, solo tienes que ^£&#$ a otros brawlers!
🔓 Cada meta requiere mil millones de eliminaciones, y tras alcanzar cada meta, las recompensas aparecerán en la tienda al día siguiente para que las reclames.
🙌 Este evento no tiene límite de recompensas, ¡solo de tiempo!

✨SORTEO ESPECIAL✨

🎫 Puedes ganar un año entero del Brawl Pass Plus, es decir, 12 pases en total, y 10 pases adicionales para que los compartas con tus amigos. 🤯
👀 ¿Cómo? Comparte tu mejor partida en tus redes sociales con el hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W y elegiremos a 5 ganadores después de que termine el evento.

pt-BR.title: NOSSO PRIMEIRO EVENTO PeG?
pt-BR.description:
Chegou o evento da comunidade PARTICIPE E GANHE! 🥵🔥

Você tem 10 dias para conseguir o máximo de recompensas possível, incluindo uma ULTRACAIXA DE TROFÉUS! 😱

🎯 Estamos contando as ELIMINAÇÕES, então você só precisa ^£#$@% os outros Brawlers!
🔓 Cada marco requer 1 bilhão de eliminações e, assim que a meta é atingida, você pode reivindicar as recompensas na próxima atualização da loja!
🙌 Não há limite de recompensas no evento, o único é o tempo!

✨SORTEIO ESPECIAL✨

🎫 Você pode ganhar um ano INTEIRO de Brawl Pass Plus (12 no total) + 10 Brawl Passes Plus para dar aos amigos! 🤯
👀 COMO? Publique sua melhor jogada nas redes sociais usando a hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W, e nós escolheremos 5 sortudos quando o evento acabar!

ja.title: ブロスタ初となるP2Wコミュニティイベント！
ja.description:
「P2W」とは「プレイ・トゥ・ウィン」の略です 🥵🔥

10日間のイベント期間中、ウルトラトロフィーボックス1個を含む報酬が無限に獲得可能です 😱

🎯 今回の目標は「撃破数」！できるだけ多くの対戦相手をブッ※※しましょう！
🔓 各目標の達成には「10億撃破」が必要です。目標を達成すると、毎日のショップ更新の際に報酬が回収可能になります！
🙌 本イベントでは報酬の獲得数に上限がありません。時間の続く限り報酬を回収しましょう！

✨特別プレゼント企画✨

🎫 ブロスタパス＋の年間パス（12カ月分）＆追加のブロスタパス＋10個（フレンドへの寄付用）をプレゼント 🤯
👀 最高のプレイ動画にハッシュタグ「#BrawlStarsP2W」を添えて、SNSに投稿しましょう。5名の幸運な当選者をイベント終了後に発表します！

zh-Hant.title: 首次「P2W」社群活動？
zh-Hant.description:
這裡的「P」，不是付費（Pay），而是代表玩（Play）！隆重介紹「玩就能贏」社群活動！🥵🔥

在10天內，大家可以盡情贏取獎勵，其中包括一個究極榮耀寶箱！😱

🎯 本次活動我們將記錄擊殺數！所以大家要做的，就是把對手的英雄都^£#$掉！
🔓 每累積10億次擊殺，即可達成一個里程碑。完成一個里程碑之後，對應的獎勵會在第二天商店刷新時出現，記得領取唷！
🙌  本次活動可獲取的獎勵不設上限，唯一的限制就是活動的持續時間！

✨ 特別抽獎活動！✨

🎫 你有機會透過抽獎活動贏得一整年的高級亂鬥通行券（總共12個），另外還有10個高級亂鬥通行券可以贈送好友！🤯
👀 如何參加？在社群媒體上分享你的遊戲精彩時刻，並且在貼文中加上hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W，我們會在活動結束後選出5位幸運玩家，送上這份驚喜！

ar.title: هل هذا حدث P2W الأول على الإطلاق لمجتمع اللعبة؟
ar.description:
إنه حدث مجتمع اللعبة ’العب للفوز‘ 🥵🔥

أمامكم 10 أيام للحصول على أكبر عدد ممكن من المكافآت، بما في ذلك صندوق 😱

🎯 نحن نتابع عدد الإطاحات، لذلك كل ما عليكم فعله هو الإطاحة بالأبطال الآخرين.
🔓 يتطلب كل إنجاز القيام بمليار إطاحة، وبعد إكمال الإنجاز يمكنكم المطالبة بالمكافآت في التحديث اليومي التالي للمتجر.
🙌 لا يوجد حد مكافآت لهذا الحدث، الحد الوحيد هو الوقت.

✨هدية خاصة✨

🎫  يمكنكم ربح سنة كاملة من Brawl Pass Plus (12 شهرًا كاملاً) + 10 تذاكر Brawl Pass Plus لمشاركتها مع أصدقائكم. 🤯
👀 كيف ذلك؟ بإرسال أفضل لحظات لعبكم على وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي باستخدام وسم #BrawlStarsP2W وسنختار الفائزين الخمسة المحظوظين بعد انتهاء الحدث.

fi.title: ENSIMMÄINEN P2W-YHTEISÖTAPAHTUMAMME?!
fi.description:
Vuorossa on... PELAA JA VOITA -YHTEISÖTAPAHTUMA! 🥵🔥

Sinulla on 10 päivää aikaa ansaita mahdollisimman monta palkintoa, joihin lukeutuu myös ULTRAPOKAALILIPAS! 😱

🎯 Laskemme tyrmäyksiä. Pistä siis töpinäksi ja ala tyrmätä muita rämäpäitä!
🔓 Jokaisen etapin avaamiseen vaaditaan miljardi tyrmäystä. Voit lunastaa palkintosi etapin suorittamista seuraavan kaupan päivittäisen päivityksen yhteydessä!
🙌  Palkintoja on tarjolla rajaton määrä. Kyse on siis nopeudesta!

✨ERITYINEN ARVONTA✨

🎫 Voit voittaa Brawl Pass Plussan KOKO VUODEKSI (yht. 12 passia) ja 10 Brawl Pass Plussaa jaettavaksi kavereidesi kanssa! 🤯
👀 MITEN? Julkaise siistein peliliikkeesi somessa tunnisteella #BrawlStarsP2W. Valitsemme 5 onnekasta voittajaa tapahtuman päätyttyä!

pl.title: NASZE PIERWSZE WYDARZENIE SPOŁECZNOŚCIOWE P2W?!
pl.description:
Przedstawiamy... WYDARZENIE SPOŁECZNOŚCIOWE GRAJ I WYGRYWAJ! 🥵🔥

Macie 10 dni, aby zdobyć jak najwięcej nagród, w tym ULTRASKRZYNKĘ PUCHARÓW! 😱

🎯 Liczą się ELIMINACJE! Waszym zadaniem jest więc ^£#$ innych Zadymiarzy!
🔓 Każdy kamień milowy wymaga 1 miliarda eliminacji, a gdy zostanie osiągnięty, nagrody można odebrać w sklepie po kolejnym codziennym odświeżeniu.
🙌 W tym wydarzeniu nie obowiązuje żaden limit nagród. Jedynym limitem jest czas!

✨ROZDANIE SPECJALNE✨

🎫 Możecie wygrać Karnety Zadymiarskie plus NA CAŁY rok (w sumie 12!) + 10 Karnetów Zadymiarskich plus do podziału ze znajomymi! 🤯
👀 JAK? Udostępnijcie swoje najlepsze rozgrywki na mediach społecznościowych, używając hasztagu #BrawlStarsP2W, a my po zakończeniu wydarzenia wybierzemy 5 szczęśliwych zwycięzców.

id.title: ACARA KOMUNITAS P2W PERTAMA?!
id.description:
Ini dia ... ACARA KOMUNITAS PLAY TO WIN! 🥵🔥

Kamu punya 10 hari untuk mendapatkan sebanyak mungkin hadiah yang mencakup KOTAK TROFI ULTRA! 😱

🎯 Jumlah TUMBANG akan dicatat! Kamu cuma perlu &=^£#~$ Jagoan lain!
🔓 Setiap ambang perlu 1 miliar tumbang dan setelah suatu ambang tercapai, kamu bisa mengambil hadiah pada penyegaran harian Toko yang berikutnya!
🙌 Hadiah di acara ini tidak terbatas, yang terbatas cuma waktunya!

✨BAGI-BAGI HADIAH SPESIAL✨

🎫 Kamu bisa mendapatkan Brawl Pass Plus untuk SEPANJANG tahun (totalnya 12!) + 10 Brawl Pass Plus untuk dibagikan kepada teman! 🤯
👀 CARANYA? Unggah permainan terbaikmu di media sosial dengan tagar #BrawlStarsP2W dan kami akan memilih 5 pemenang beruntung setelah acara berakhir!

zh-Hans.title: 首次“P2W”社区活动？
zh-Hans.description:
这里的“P”，不是付费（Pay），而是代表玩（Play）！隆重介绍“玩就能赢”社区活动！🥵🔥

在10天内，大家可以尽情赢取奖励，其中包括一个究极荣誉宝箱！😱

🎯 本次活动我们将记录击倒数！所以大家要做的，就是把对手的英雄都^£#$掉！
🔓 每累积10亿次击倒，即可达成一个里程碑。完成一个里程碑之后，对应的奖励会在第二天商店刷新时出现，记得领取哦！
🙌 本次活动可获取的奖励不设上限，唯一的限制就是活动的持续时间！

✨ 特别赠礼活动！✨

🎫 你有机会通过赠礼活动赢得一整年的高级乱斗金券（总共12个），另外还有10个高级乱斗金券可以赠送给好友！🤯
👀 如何参加？在社交媒体上分享你的游戏高光时刻，并且在贴文中加上话题标签#BrawlStarsP2W，我们会在活动结束后选出5位幸运玩家，送上惊喜赠礼！

nl.title: ONS ALLEREERSTE P2W-COMMUNITYEVENEMENT?!
nl.description:
Het is het... 'PLAY TO WIN'-COMMUNITYEVENEMENT! 🥵🔥

Je hebt 10 dagen de tijd om zo veel mogelijk beloningen te krijgen, waaronder een ULTRA-TROFEEËNDOOS! 😱

🎯 We tellen UITSCHAKELINGEN, dus het enige wat je hoeft te doen is andere knokkers ^£#*@$!
🔓 Elke mijlpaal vereist 1 miljard uitschakelingen en na het voltooien van een mijlpaal, kun je de beloningen claimen bij de volgende dagelijkse winkel-reset!
🙌 Er is geen beloningenlimiet voor dit evenement. De enige limiet is tijd!

✨SPECIALE WEGGEEFACTIE✨

🎫 Je kunt een HEEL jaar aan Brawl Pass Plus winnen (12 in totaal) + 10 Brawl Passes Plus om te delen met je vrienden! 🤯
👀 HOE? Post je beste gameplay op sociale media met de hashtag #BrawlStarsP2W en wij kiezen de 5 gelukkige winnaars nadat het evenement afloopt!

snippet.title: China Hits Back: TikTok, Boeing & Rare Earths in US Trade War | Vantage with Palki Sharma | N18G
snippet.description:
China Hits Back: TikTok, Boeing & Rare Earths in US Trade War | Vantage with Palki Sharma | N18G

China is no longer playing defence in the trade war—it’s going after American consumers, brands, and technology. Chinese factories are flooding TikTok with factory-price videos targeting US shoppers and mocking Western brands. At the same time, China has suspended rare earth exports and frozen Boeing deliveries. President Xi Jinping, now touring Southeast Asia, is positioning China as a global partner—while calling out US “bullying.” As tensions rise, the fight is no longer just about tariffs. It’s being waged online, in markets, and in minds. This is a global clash like no other.

---

snippet.title: King Gizzard & The Lizard Wizard - Deadstick (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Phantom Island is out June 13, 2025 on http://www.pdoomrecords.com/

Director / Editor: Guy Tyzack
Co-Director: Ambrose Kenny-Smith
Cinematographer/Colour grader: Tom Dunphy 
Produced by Guy Tyzack & Tom Dunphy
Super 8 DOP: Guy Tyzack 
Camera Assistant: Christy Chudosnik
Costume Designer: Caity Westlake
Runner: Zac Main
Makeup: Nadine Muller
Prosthetics: April Thurrowgood
Aeroplane build: Boxwars
16mm film processing: Neglab
Super 8 film processing: Nanolab
Film scanning: Memorylab
Eshay: Lilgerbs
Strongman: Ryger G Miles
Flight attendant: Hayley Mayall
Swing Dancers: Miyako Miyazaki, Josh Varcoe, Steph Ashby, Joel Kohn, Kate Bray, Chris Sutton, Gabby Urban, Nick Ellis Friedl

--
Initial band recording by Sam Joseph
Orchestral arrangement by Chad Kelly
Orchestral recording by Lachlan Carrick and Ross Cockle
Orchestra conducted by Brett Kelly
Overdubs by King Gizzard
Mixed by Stu Mackenzie
Produced by Stu Mackenzie
Mastered by Joe Carra

Amby: Piano, Vocals
Cavs: Drums, Percussion
Cookie: Organ
Joey: Guitar, Vocals
Lukey: Bass
Stu: Guitar, Mellotron, Vocals

Orchestral Contractors – Roscoe Irwin, Cameron Jamieson
Musical Consultant – Roscoe Irwin
Saxophone: Tim Wilson, Lachlan Davidson, Phil Noy
Trumpet: Patrick McMullin, Daniel Beasy, Shane Hooton
Trombone: Chris Vizard, James Bowman, Joe O’Callaghan


DEADSTICK
There once flew a pilot, high and free
Danced with the clouds
Pirouetted with the breeze
But out of synch to the mechanical beat that pulsed at the heart of the metal machine
Thought of their partner and thought of their kids
Thought where they’re going and thought where they’d been
But a subtle change
The routine shattered
Prepare the mind
Arrange the matters

Deadstick
Deadstick
I’m a bird with a broken wing
Deadstick (deadstick)
Deadstick (deadstick)
This nightingale can’t sing

I wake with a retch to the smell of ammonia and my eyes start watering
A shadow?
A body?
“Who are you?” I say when a voice cracks like a frozen lake
“I am your child,
You are my mother and I’m sitting here dying”
I say “I got no children, I am but a boy, you are mistaken

”She sings “Follow me down through the wind and the earth
to the edge of the forgotten seas”
“Save me from the hurt”
“Tell me of my worth”
“A phantom is taking everything”

Deadstick
Death wish
Panic in the cockpit
Praying in the cabin
We’re all holding hands
Deadstick
Death wish
Lost all propulsive
Propellers ain’t spinning
Being forced to land
Deadstick
Death wish
We’re shutting off the engines
Blues skies are turning a darker grey
Deadstick
Death wish
Heading for the smoking hole in the airfield I can’t locate

Mayday! Mayday! Mayday! Save me!
I’m in a tight spot
Catastrophe
Mayday! Mayday! Mayday! Save me!
I’m ‘bout to make a crash landing

Deadstick
Deadstick
I’m a bird with a broken wing
Deadstick
Deadstick
This nightingale can’t sing
Yeah!

Deadstick
Death wish
I can’t believe we made it out alive
Deadstick
Death wish
Send me help before I die

snippet.title: The Biggest Misconception In Physics
snippet.description:
Why does energy disappear in General Relativity? 👉 Use code VERITASIUM to get 50% off your first monthly KiwiCo Crate! https://www.kiwico.com/VERITASIUM 

Try Snatoms! A molecular modelling kit I invented where the atoms snap together.
https://ve42.co/SnatomsV 

▀▀▀
A huge thank you to Prof. Geraint Lewis, Prof. Melissa Franklin, Prof. David Kaiser, Elba Alonso-Monsalve, Richard Behiel, Prof. Leo Stein and Jakob Schwintenberg for their invaluable expertise and contributions to this video. 

Special thanks to Alessandro from ScienceClic for his help on animations and input on the script. Check out his excellent video on Noether’s theorem here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hF_uHfSoOGA 

▀▀▀
0:00 What is symmetry?
4:25 Emmy Noether and Einstein
7:33 General Covariance
11:59 The Principle of Least Action
15:29 Noether’s First Theorem
18:24 The Continuity Equation
23:20 Escape from Germany
24:49 The Standard Model - Higgs and Quarks

▀▀▀

Elizaveta Litvinova via Wikipedia - https://ve42.co/LitvinovaE
Sofya Kovalevskaya via Wikipedia - https://ve42.co/KovalevskayaS
Charlotte Scott via Wikipedia - https://ve42.co/ScottC
Cornelia Fabri via Wikipedia - https://ve42.co/FabriC
Emmy Noether, the renowned mathematician who taught 20 years of unpaid classes just because she was a woman via english.elpais.com - https://ve42.co/NoetherPay

Noether, E. (1983). Invariante Variationsprobleme. Gott.Nachr.1918:235-257,1918; Transp.Theory Statist.Phys.1:186-207,1971 - https://ve42.co/InvarProb

De Haro, S. (2021). Noether’s Theorems and Energy in General Relativity. Cambridge University Press, 2021 - https://ve42.co/EnergyGR
Rowe, D. E. (2019). Emmy Noether on Energy Conservation in General Relativity. arXiv - https://ve42.co/EnergyCon
Branding, K. (2005). A Note on General Relativity, Energy Conservation, and Noether’s Theorems. Springer - https://ve42.co/GRanEC

Additional References:
https://ve42.co/NoethersAdRefs

snippet.title: Vice President JD Vance drops Ohio State's national championship trophy at White House event
snippet.description:
Ohio State, who won the title in January after navigating the first 12-team College Football Playoff, will be the sport’s first champion to make the traditional visit since Donald Trump's return to the presidency for a second term.

The last time Ohio State's football team visited the White House to celebrate a playoff championship was in 2015 when former President Barack Obama was in office.

snippet.title: Here, Tomorrow (ft Lilas, Kevin Penkin) - Spirit Blossom Beyond ‘25 S2 Cinematic - League of Legends
snippet.description:
Around every light, a shadow. Beyond every ending, a beginning.


Enter the world of Spirit Blossom Beyond during Season 2, starting April 30, 2025 at 11 AM PDT, and follow Xin Zhao’s saga in the first of two motion comics on May 14, 2025.

Music Video: Created in partnership with THE LINE

LISTEN NOW: league.ffm.to/heretomorrow

Music Credits:
“Here, Tomorrow”
Featured Artist: Lilas
Composed by: Kevin Penkin
Written by: Kevin Penkin
Lyrics by: Christopher Keith O’Neill, Elspeth Bawden, Fabian Malabello
Music Production by: Kevin Penkin, Matthew Mclean
Mixed by: Matthew Mclean
Mastered by: Jett Galindo
Executive Produced and Supervised by: Riot Music Team


Vocals recorded at Birdie House, Tokyo
Vocals performed by: Lilas Ikuta
Vocal recording engineer: Kunio Nishikawara
Vocal direction by: Elspeth Bawden, Keita Konnie Aoki (EVOQUE Inc.), Kevin Penkin
Project Supervisor: Fabian Malabello

Orchestra recorded at Hollywood Scoring, Los Angeles
Orchestra Conductor: Bill Hemstapat
Orchestra Contractor: Noah Gladstone
Recording Engineer: Adam Michalak
Assistant Engineer: Ryan Nelson
Orchestration: Edward Trybek, Jonathan Beard, and Henri Wilkinson for Tutti Music Partners
Preparation: Jordan Cox, James Regan, and Brad Ritchie
Recording Coordinator: Noah Gladstone

Solo Shakuhachi: Zac Zinger
Solo Harp: Alison Bjorkedal

Violin
Luanne Homzy, concertmaster
YuEun Kim, principal
Mark Robertson
Katie Sloan
Mui-Yee Chu
Leah Zeger
Sam Fischer

Sarah Thornblade

Dana Zulpykhar

Viola

Timothy Loo, principal

Bass

Clarinet

Jonathan Sacdalan

French Horn
Dylan Hart, principal
Laura Brenes
Allen Fogle
Teag Reaves

Kevin Penkin is represented by: Fabian Malabello [The Otherworld Agency]

Lilas Ikuta is represented by: Yohei Yashiro, Shuya Yamamoto, Asami Yoshino, Kai Kamata, Nina Shimono, [Echoes / Sony Music Entertainment (Japan) Inc.], Todd Matsumoto [Creative Artists Agency]

P/C Riot Games 2025

Lyrics:

Echoes from beyond the past
The seed is sowed
The spirit knows
May it guide me for

I again, will wander far
And shape the path,
To meet again
On veiled horizons

Ah__
The wind is calling your name
A whisper of the souls who never leave you
Ah__
Collect your silver tears
And pray they disappear, tomorrow

Earth and ether to combine
The light, it shows
The dark, it knows, our tethers

Spirits haunt the restless mind
But seek to find
We’ll meet again
Can’t you hear them?

Ah__
The wind is calling your name
A whisper of the souls who never leave us
Ah__
Collect your silver tears
And pray that we are here, tomorrow

Ah__
Can’t you hear the call?

Ah__
The wind is calling my name
A whisper of the souls who never leave me
Ah__
Collect your silver tears
And pray I reappear, tomorrow


League of Legends - Free Download & Play
https://signup.leagueoflegends.com/


#HereTomorrow #SpiritBlossom #LeagueofLegends

snippet.title: LIVE: Blue Origin launches Katy Perry, Gayle King to space

The crew comprises of singer Katy Perry, TV journalist Gayle King, former TV journalist and Bezos’ fiancee Lauren Sanchez, former NASA rocket scientist Aisha Bowe, research scientist Amanda Nguyen and movie producer Kerianne Flynn. #blueorigin #katyperry #space #live 

Credit: Blue Origin

snippet.title: Rory McIlroy’s Final Round | Every Single Shot | The 2025 Masters
snippet.description:
Every single shot from every single hole of 2025 Masters Champion Rory McIlroy's Final Round. #themasters

---

Since 1934, the Masters Tournament has been home to some of golf’s greatest moments. Amidst blooming azaleas, towering pines and flowering dogwoods, the first full week of April ushers in a stage unique to golf and to sport. Over four days and 72 holes, the smallest field in major championship golf competes for a chance to capture the Green Jacket and a place in Masters history.

---

snippet.description:
we need to talk...

2ND CHANNEL: https://bit.ly/3v1ZJPV

MERCH: https://shop.charlottedobre.net/

CREDITS - FOLLOW THE CREATORS!

Hey ya'll! After years of reacting to your wildest stories, dramatic Reddit posts, and the internet’s most chaotic moments — it’s time for a bit of a shift. This channel has been such a fun ride, but I’ve been feeling like it’s time for something more. A new chapter. A fresh vibe.

In this video, I’m opening up about the future of the Charlotte Dobre channel — what’s staying, what’s changing, and where we’re going next. Whether you’ve been here since day one or just found the chaos recently, I’m so grateful you’re part of this community. 💜

Change can be scary, but it can also be really freaking exciting. Let’s take this next step together.

Subscribe if you haven’t already and drop your thoughts in the comments — I want to hear from you!

#charlottedobre #channelupdate #announcementvideo #newchapter #youtubedirection #charlottedobrereacts #thankyoucommunity #creatorupdate #bignews

Hi, I'm Charlotte Dobre. I'm an actor, reactor, singer and sometimes (not really) comedian. On this channel I do reactions, commentary and occasionally I make a joke or two. I love poking fun at social media, weddings, entitled people, tiktok and OF COURSE petty people. I upload daily, usually 7 days a week, unless life gets crazy or I get lazy. Come hang out, it's a good time.

snippet.title: Taskmaster Series 19 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Eureka! It’s a new series of #Taskmaster! Your five volatile elements are Fatiha El-Ghorri, Jason Mantzoukas, Mathew Baynton, Rosie Ramsey and Stevie Martin - plus, of course, a compound of Daviesium and Horneium.

Thursday 1st May at 9pm on Channel 4 and 2nd May around the world on YouTube. 🧪

------------

Watch full episodes in the UK on http://Channel4.com
Buy Taskmaster merch: https://taskmasterstore.com/

------------

In this Broadcast Award-winning, BAFTA and Emmy Award-nominated entertainment show, Taskmaster tyrant Greg Davies (Man Down, Cuckoo), with the help of his loyal assistant Alex Horne (The Horne Section and the show’s creator), sets out to test the wiles, wit and wisdom of five hyper-competitive comedians.

Comedians that have risked life, limb, and dignity in the hope of making the Taskmaster proud so far include: Frank Skinner (The Frank Skinner Show), Mel Giedroyc (The Great British Bake Off), Romesh Ranganathan (Asian Provocateur), Hugh Dennis (Outnumbered), Sally Phillips (Bridget Jones’ Diary), Rose Matafeo (Edinburgh Comedy Award Winner 2018), and Russell Howard (The Russell Howard Hour). Unaware of what awaits them in each wax-sealed envelope, only one competitor can become the victorious owner of His Royal Task-ness’ golden head and be crowned the next Taskmaster Champion.

#Taskmaster #Comedy #GregDavies #AlexHorne

snippet.title: the diabolical decline of Fisch.
snippet.description:
i didn't talk about the updates or anything else like that because I just wasn't there to experience them (and the video wouldve been too long, MIGHT make a part 2)

I'm pretty late to the party with this video but I felt like I should make it, especially since I cared about the game enough to put over 120 hours into it and made two videos about it. It was nice having a game to play and enjoy that didn't involve fighting people or spending money, but I guess good things can't last forever. I talked to a few hardcore fischers to make sure everything in the video is as accurate as possible, if there's some misinformation or something I missed, I'll point it out in the description or just cut it out

snippet.title: Stadium Gameplay Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
Forge your victory in our brand new permanent game mode, Stadium!

Strategy, teamwork, and hero evolution will determine who wins in Stadium as you and your team battle it out in this best-of-7, round-based mode.

In each round, players will be able to earn Stadium Cash that can be used to unlock powerful, game-changing abilities. Players can also take down high-value enemies marked with bounties to earn bonus Stadium Cash and turn the tide of battle.

See your hero’s upgraded abilities in action with the option to play in third-person or maintain the classic first-person perspective. The choice is yours!

Stadium also features its own standalone ranking system with season-exclusive rewards, encouraging players to master the mode and prove their competitive dominance.

Step into the arena when Season 16: Stadium launches on Apr 22.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
_

snippet.title: 5 Lego Walkers vs 7 Obstacles
snippet.description:
5 Lego walkers are tested against different obstacles. Which one is the winner? Enjoy!

0:00 Obstacle 1: gap (10 cm)
0:27 Obstacle 2: step (2.5 cm)
0:53 Obstacle 3: drop (9 cm)
1:21 Obstacle 4: u-turn on rough surface
2:17 Obstacle 5: pillars
2:55 Obstacle 6: triangle hill (30 deg inclination)
3:40 Obstacle 7: triangle valley (35 deg inclination)

List of vehicles:
  Simple 2-legged walker (no steering)
  2-legged walker (2 legs + base for walking, a tail leg for turning)
  4-legged walker
  8-legged walker (Klann linkage)
  16-legged walker

All walkers have tennis grip on the soles of their feet.

Building 5 Lego Walkers:
https://youtu.be/LOJuK3eR8FM

snippet.title: Elephant Teaches 20 Lions That He's The King
snippet.description:
Deon Kelbrick filmed this curiously one-sided interaction and sent it to Latest Sightings. It occurred at the viewpoint on the H1-3, just north of Tshokwane Picnic Site in the Kruger National Park.

Join our channel to get access to EXTENDED and UNEDITED videos:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyfZleh4w7buTzi0WfY8WqA/join

Send in your wildlife video here, and earn money: https://latestsightings.com/film-earn

Deon's series of video clips began by setting the scene. A large pride of twenty lions lay spread out on the bank of a dry riverbed.

The pride consists of a mature male, several lionesses and cubs of various ages. Renowned for their strength, both individually and collectively, you would think that nothing would disturb their late morning nap.

While most of the pride rested peacefully, three of them either heard or smelt something that got their attention. Moving away from the group, they went to investigate.

Subsequently, rising up from the riverbed, appeared a young, lone elephant bull.

On reaching maturity, male elephants leave their natal herds, so this was not unusual in itself. But more about that later.

As the oversized gate-crasher came into view, the three lions tensed up. Lions are known to prey on lone elephants in some places, but seldom in Kruger Park.

And it would be no different on this day. Seeing that the bull was heading directly towards them, the three lions gave way.

It was clear that the elephant was well aware of the lions' presence. Ears flared and head held upright, the bull lengthened his stride as he made straight towards them.

When he got within twenty metres of the pride, he pulled up to assess the situation. And, to give the big cats a chance to leave of their own accord.

In response, some members of the pride got to their feet and sauntered off. Meanwhile, others remained where they were, not ready to exert themselves until the bull made his next move.

Not impressed by the lions' failure to give way immediately, the elephant took things up a notch. Showing surprising acceleration, the bull charged, trumpeting loudly as he did.

Every member of the pride, from the dominant male to the youngest cub, immediately took off in the opposite direction.

Soon enough, the elephant decided that he had made his point. Pulling up, once again, he tracked the movement of a lioness who had splintered from the pride in the chaos.

Later, satisfied that she too did not dispute his supremacy, the bull ripped up a tussock of grass to chew on.

Apparently not liking the taste of his snack, he promptly wandered off.
As for the lions, seeing their tormentor waddle off without a care in the world, they soon returned to where they had lain earlier.

If lions could talk, you can be sure none of them was about to mention anything about being 'king of the jungle'.

In both lion and elephant communities, adult males play little to no role in raising their offspring. Their contribution in this respect is limited to security and DNA. In both instances, when they reach sexual maturity, they are forced (generally by dominant males in the area) to leave their mothers.
Usually, they will band with other males to form bachelor groups or alliances, from which they derive mutual protection. This affords them an environment in which to grow stronger and wiser, thereby enhancing their chances of reproductive success when fully matured.

No doubt, this young bull's experience will have helped build his confidence, shaping his character for a long life ahead.
 
To license the footage: 
Contact@LatestSightings.com

Snapchat: LatestSightings
Twitter & Instagram: @LatestKruger

For live wildlife sightings in the Kruger National Park: http://www.latestsightings.com/

And like our Facebook page for great sightings and photos: https://www.facebook.com/latestsightingskruger

Subscribe to us on YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/LatestSightings

It was clear that the elephant was well aware of the lions' presence. Ears flared and head held upright, the bull lengthened his stride as he made straight towards them.

When he got within twenty metres of the pride, he pulled up to assess the situation. And, to give the big cats a chance to leave of their own accord.

In response, some members of the pride got to their feet and sauntered off. Meanwhile, others remained where they were, not ready to exert themselves until the bull made his next move.

Not impressed by the lions' failure to give way immediately, the elephant took things up a notch. Showing surprising acceleration, the bull charged, trumpeting loudly as he did.

Every member of the pride, from the dominant male to the youngest cub, immediately took off in the opposite direction.

Soon enough, the elephant decided that he had made his point. Pulling up, once again, he tracked the movement of a lioness who had splintered from the pride in the chaos.

Later, satisfied that she too did not dispute his supremacy, the bull ripped up a tussock of grass to chew on.

Apparently not liking the taste of his snack, he promptly wandered off.
As for the lions, seeing their tormentor waddle off without a care in the world, they soon returned to where they had lain earlier.

If lions could talk, you can be sure none of them was about to mention anything about being 'king of the jungle'.

In both lion and elephant communities, adult males play little to no role in raising their offspring. Their contribution in this respect is limited to security and DNA. In both instances, when they reach sexual maturity, they are forced (generally by dominant males in the area) to leave their mothers.
Usually, they will band with other males to form bachelor groups or alliances, from which they derive mutual protection. This affords them an environment in which to grow stronger and wiser, thereby enhancing their chances of reproductive success when fully matured.

No doubt, this young bull's experience will have helped build his confidence, shaping his character for a long life ahead.

snippet.title: After the Winning Putt | Rory McIlroy Captures His First Masters Win
snippet.description:
Rory McIlroy is overcome with emotion after winning the sudden death playoff at the 89th Masters Tournament. #themasters

---

Since 1934, the Masters Tournament has been home to some of golf’s greatest moments. Amidst blooming azaleas, towering pines and flowering dogwoods, the first full week of April ushers in a stage unique to golf and to sport. Over four days and 72 holes, the smallest field in major championship golf competes for a chance to capture the Green Jacket and a place in Masters history.

---

snippet.title: The 2025 Green Jacket Ceremony | The Masters
snippet.description:
Rory McIlroy is awarded his Green Jacket following his 2025 Masters championship victory. #themasters 

---

Since 1934, the Masters Tournament has been home to some of golf’s greatest moments. Amidst blooming azaleas, towering pines and flowering dogwoods, the first full week of April ushers in a stage unique to golf and to sport. Over four days and 72 holes, the smallest field in major championship golf competes for a chance to capture the Green Jacket and a place in Masters history.

---

View scores, player information, patron information, watch live and more: https://masters.com 
Follow @themasters on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/themasters/

snippet.title: ARGENTINA vs. BRASIL [4-1] | RESUMEN | ELIMINATORIAS SUDAMERICANAS | FECHA 14
snippet.description:
¡Goleada de #Argentina en el clásico! 👏🇦🇷

#EliminatoriasSudamericanas #Argentina 4 - 1 #Brasil 

El primer gol llegó ya a los 4’, De Paul inició la acción, la continuó Thiago Almada, que asistió con un pase entre líneas para la llegada por el centro de Álvarez, que le ganó a pura potencia a los centrales brasileño para definir entre las piernas de Bento.

La Albiceleste pareció tomar nota de las ganas de Brasil de igualar el encuentro y jugó una primera parte de alto nivel, en la que redujo a la Verdeamarelha, a partir de un juego dinámico, con mucho toque entre líneas, paciencia para controlar la pelota y claridad para atacar.

Así llegó el segundo tanto, una jugada en la que la Albiceleste tocó la pelota de un área a la otra, en la que sus once jugadores dieron pases durante más de un minuto y medio hasta que Nicolás Molina recibió por la derecha, envió el centro cruzado y Enzo Fernández entró a espaldas de la zaga visitante para estampar el 2-0 a los 12’.

Brasil no encontraba la llave para entrar en el partido, pero tuvo la suerte de un error del ‘Cuti’ Romero, quien falló en una salida y propició el descuento con un derechazo de Matheus Cunha a los 26’.

El equipo de Dorival insinuó un intento de ir por más, apareció Vinicius Júnior con un par de incursiones por la izquierda, pero Argentina asimiló bien el descuento y retomó el dominio, coronando un buen primer tiempo con el gol de Mac Allister para ampliar la ventaja a los 37’.

En la segunda parte llegó con el gol de Giuliano Simeone, que celebró su primer tanto con la Albiceleste tras un centro de Tagliafico a los 71’, apenas tres minutos después de ingresar.

En la próxima fecha, a jugarse en junio, Argentina visitará a Chile, mientras que Brasil acudirá a Ecuador.

Suscríbete I Inscreva-se I Subscribe: http://bit.ly/CONMEBOL

snippet.title: White Lotus' Aimee Lou Wood SLAMS SNL for Mocking Her Appearance and Accent
snippet.description: 'The White Lotus' Aimee Lou Wood calls out 'SNL' for mocking her appearance and accent in posts on Instagram. During Jon Hamm's hosting gig, the late-night show featured a parody of the HBO series with a political spin. Despite the sketch spoofing real-life politicians as White Lotus guests, 'SNL' took aim at Aimee's portrayal of 'Chelsea,' which the actress is now calling 'mean and unfunny.'

snippet.title: OK Go - Love (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Get this song:  https://sym.ffm.to/andtheadjacentpossible
And all things OK Go: https://linktr.ee/okgomusic

In this mini-documentary by our partners at the Project Management Institute, you’ll see the whole process and meet the brilliant, creative people that made it possible: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_EKQKF4qPPI&ab_channel=ProjectManagementInstitute%28PMI%29

In this Universal Robots piece, you’ll learn more about the incredible technology team and their battalion of dancing machines: https://www.universal-robots.com/en-us/landing-pages/syncing-30-robots-to-a-beat-the-making-of-ok-go-s-love-music-video

And if you want to know what it felt like from our perspective, check this out. We wore Ray-Ban Meta glasses throughout the shoot so you can see it through our eyes: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQufZQMXUhY&ab_channel=OKGo

Lyrics:
Light cast so long before sound, before song
falls on your eyes and the dance starts again

And in this grand ballroom of nothingness
your hand so warm with somethingness
we whirl and twirl and music’s invented again 
In this grand ballroom of nothingness
we soar, we sail to the only song there’s ever been: Love
The only song there’s ever been’s just begun: Love
The only song there’s ever been plays again: Love
It’s love

How marvelous just to be anything,
circling the hall to divine harmony

And in this grand ballroom of nothingness
your hand so warm with somethingness
we swirl, unfurl, and music’s invented again 
In this grand ballroom of nothingness
we soar, we sail to the only song there’s ever been: Love
The only song there’s ever been’s just begun: Love
The only song there’s ever been plays again: Love
The only song there’s ever been never ends: Love

And against such staggering odds of anything at all
that lonely poet Chance called the dance and built the hall 
and, with such modest hands, drew up plans and gave us all

Love

And all things OK Go: https://linktr.ee/okgomusic

In this mini-documentary by our partners at the Project Management Institute, you’ll see the whole process and meet the brilliant, creative people that made it possible: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_EKQKF4qPPI&ab_channel=ProjectManagementInstitute%28PMI%29

In this Universal Robots piece, you’ll learn more about the incredible technology team and their battalion of dancing machines: https://www.universal-robots.com/en-us/landing-pages/syncing-30-robots-to-a-beat-the-making-of-ok-go-s-love-music-video

And if you want to know what it felt like from our perspective, check this out. We wore Ray-Ban Meta glasses throughout the shoot so you can see it through our eyes: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQufZQMXUhY&ab_channel=OKGo

Lyrics:
Light cast so long before sound, before song
falls on your eyes and the dance starts again

And in this grand ballroom of nothingness
your hand so warm with somethingness
we whirl and twirl and music’s invented again 
In this grand ballroom of nothingness
we soar, we sail to the only song there’s ever been: Love
The only song there’s ever been’s just begun: Love
The only song there’s ever been plays again: Love
It’s love

How marvelous just to be anything,
circling the hall to divine harmony

And in this grand ballroom of nothingness
your hand so warm with somethingness
we swirl, unfurl, and music’s invented again 
In this grand ballroom of nothingness
we soar, we sail to the only song there’s ever been: Love
The only song there’s ever been’s just begun: Love
The only song there’s ever been plays again: Love
The only song there’s ever been never ends: Love

And against such staggering odds of anything at all
that lonely poet Chance called the dance and built the hall 
and, with such modest hands, drew up plans and gave us all

Love

#MinecraftMovie #Minecraft

Tracklist:
1. I Feel Alive - Jack Black
2. When I'm Gone ("A Minecraft Movie" Version) - Dirty Honey
3. Change Song - Dayglow
4. Zero to Hero - BENEE
5. Could This Be Love? - Bret McKenzie
6. Just Can't Get Enough (from "A Minecraft Movie”) [Instrumental Version] - Jamieson Shaw
7. Steve's Lava Chicken - Jack Black
8. Birthday Rap - Jack Black & Jason Momoa
9. Ode to Dennis - Jack Black
10. Minecraft (from “A Minecraft Movie”) - Mark Mothersbaugh
11. Mintage  - Mark Mothersbaugh
12. Midport Village - Mark Mothersbaugh
13. Day to Night - Mark Mothersbaugh
14. Steve in The Nether - Mark Mothersbaugh
15. Chicken Fight Club - Mark Mothersbaugh
16. I Need a Win, Man - Mark Mothersbaugh
17. I'm Coming With / Minecraft - Mark Mothersbaugh
18. Nitwit Crosses and Steve Finds / Minecraft - Mark Mothersbaugh
19. Woodland Mansion Planning - Mark Mothersbaugh
20. Steve vs. Malgosha - Mark Mothersbaugh
21. Piglins Attack - Mark Mothersbaugh
22. Heroic Henry / Minecraft - Mark Mothersbaugh
23. Let's Go Fight Some Pigs - Mark Mothersbaugh
24. Run from the Great Hog - Mark Mothersbaugh
25. Back in The Nether - Mark Mothersbaugh

About A Minecraft Movie: 
From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, A Minecraft Movie, directed by Jared Hess, is the first ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time. Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn't just help you craft, it's essential to one's survival! Four misfits—Garrett "The Garbage Man" Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they'll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative…the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world.

About WaterTower Music:
WaterTower Music, the in-house label for the WarnerMedia companies, releases recorded music as rich and diverse as the companies themselves. It has been the soundtrack home to many of the world’s most iconic films, television shows and games since 2001. Featured releases include the soundtracks for Aquaman, The Hobbit, Interstellar, Game of Thrones, Crazy Rich Asians, King Arthur, Zack Snyder’s Justice League, Westworld and Dune.

snippet.title: Rauw Alejandro - Carita Linda (Official Video)
snippet.description:
www.caritalinda.com 

Lyrics:
Wow que linda tu estás 
Yo solo te miro a ti 
La combinación de tu boca 
Con este tequila a la roca 
Son mortal pa’ mi 

Siento que ya estuve aquí una vez 
No sé si te pasa lo mismo a ti también 
Amores van amores vienen 
Pero que más da 
Si al final cada quien merece lo que da 

Bajo las estrellas 
La luna llena 
Tú eres mi calma en esta tempestad 
Hay caritas lindas que dejan huellas 
y la tuya no se puede borrar 

Como me gustas tú a mi 
Como me gustas tú a mi 
Quisiera hablarte de otro tema 
Que con las palabras no puedo decir 
Por qué no nos vamos de aquí (es más)
Por qué no nos vamos a vivir
A una casita en la arena y nunca mudarnos de ahí 
De ahí

bridge…

(Cosa nuestra )

Ella baila sola 
Y yo la veo 
Tú tienes un swing 
Tienes un piquete 
Tú tiene’ un meneo 
Ponte peligrosa que 
Yo siempre me atrevo 
Si jugamos al juego de quien se enamora 
yo pierdo primero 
Y vuelvo a caer (no)
No me puedo contener (no)
A tu carita de bandida 
Y como me miras 
Me pones a delirar 
Cositas imaginar 

Cúcame mujer
 “Ee-feh… mee… shee oh… n go-keh.”
Yuba cuembe
pa’ que lo baile usted.

Es una locura amarte
Desde la primera vez 
Durmiendo a mi lao 
Te quiero todas las noches 

Bajo las estrellas 
La luna llena 
Tú eres mi calma en esta tempestad 
Hay caritas lindas que dejan huellas 
y la tuya no se puede borrar 

Como me gusta tú a mi 
Como me gustas tú a mi 
Quisiera hablarte de otro tema 
Que con las palabras no puedo decir 
Por qué no nos vamos de aquí (es mas)
Por qué no nos vamos a vivir
A una casita de arena y nunca mudarnos de ahí
De ahí

….

Mi Niña hermosa yo vine a ver 
Como corre la tormenta yo vine a ver 
Ay niñita linda yo vine a ver 
Como corre la tormenta yo vine a ver 


Ahí viene la tormenta yo vine a ver 
Con la niña hermosa la quiero ver 
Esas caras bonitas yo vine a ver 
Como corre la tormenta yo vine a ver

Casa productora: ABSNT
Productor Ejecutivo: Martin Seipel
Jefa de producción: Rocio Taboada
Director de Fotografía: Franklin Ricart

A ella le gusta y yo soy su monrrero

Ella está puesta pa' mí, eso me motiva
